\newlabel{fig:flip-rate}{{2}{7}{Flip rate (\%) vs.\ number of patched neurons $k$ on a log-scale x-axis, averaged over 15 cells (5 folds $\times $ 3 seeds). Grey band: min--max envelope of random-$k$ baseline flip rates. Instruction-tuned generators (blue) and base generators (red) both sit well above the random baseline at every $k$}{figure.caption.6}{}}
